des: This skill suggests a morning routine. It suits people who work Monday to Friday and have off on weekends. The routine is leaned on suggestions on how a routine could be to have a productive day. It helps people who have a hard time building a morning routine and for others who have a hard time deciding planning. Every morning routine is different and varies from one person to another but this routine helps to build habits which you then can integrate in your own routine.
